name: o11.1 — Mundanity — rev.04.2
description: Herd mentality vs your way. You know that you will get what is yours, and the only thing which you should listen to is your inner voice. But what is your inner voice, and what is a masterfully targeted advertisement? Since we are on the topic, what is your self, if not a sophisticated combination of past experiences and the messages put in your head throughout your life?
